---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Devika Exim - Dried Red Chillies Exporters in Guntur"
  description="Welcome to Devika Exim, best quality Guntur dried red chillies and chilli powder exporters. We trade and export dry red both retail and wholesale straight from Guntur."
  canonical="https://devikaexim.in"
>

    <div class="n-media-container">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <div class="centered-heading">
          <h1>
            DEVIKA EXIM
            <span class="underline"></span>
          </h1>
        </div>

        <div class="intro-text">

          <p>
            At Devika Exim, we specialize in <strong>exporting</strong> and selling the finest quality <strong>dried red chillies and chilli powder</strong> directly from Guntur. Whether you need chillies for <strong>retail or wholesale,</strong> we offer the best prices in the market. Our secret lies in sourcing directly from local farmers in the famous Guntur Mirchi Market Yard, known worldwide for producing the spiciest and most flavorful chillies.

            By working closely with farmers, we ensure that our customers get fresh, high-quality chillies at unbeatable prices. Whether you're looking for bulk orders for your business or smaller quantities for personal use, our chillies will add that perfect kick of heat to your dishes.

            Known as the Chilli Capital of India, Guntur's red chillies are rich in color, spice, and flavor, making them a top choice for culinary experts and food lovers around the world. From mild to extra hot, our varieties suit every taste and need.

            Exporting worldwide, we take pride in providing fast, reliable service with every order. If you’re looking for <strong>best dried chillies at the lowest prices</strong>, you’ve come to the right place.


          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class='tagline'>
      <h4>Best Guntur Dry Red Chillies & Chilli Powder <br /> Retail and Wholesale Exporter</h4>
    </div>

    <!-- top buttons -->
    <div class="n-mbr-section-btn">

      <button type="button" class="n-btn n-place-order-btn"
        onclick="zforms_open_window('https://forms.zohopublic.com/gunturredchillies1/form/Contactus/formperma/dRNXAbE0AMFcrUjQhR4AfgxQx3IIyKT0sUfu1ZbNWzY', 648, 700); return false;">
        Place Order Now
      </button>

      <a class="n-btn n-check-prices-btn" href="/blog.html">
        Check Today's Prices
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- contactcard -->
    <div class="n-media-container-row">
      <h2>
        <span>
          Contact Us for Bulk Wholesale Orders
        </span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        We offer flexible wholesale &amp; retail orders and can supply listed products in any quantity to
        meet
        your
        needs.
        <br />
        <span>
          For quicker responses, please contact us via WhatsApp.
        </span>
      </p>

    </div>

    <div class="export-info">
      <p>Currently exporting Guntur Red Dry Chillies across India, with plans to expand into international markets soon.</p>
    </div>

    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Spice Up Your World with Premium Guntur Red Chillies</h1>
        <p>Premium Quality, Unbeatable Prices, Fresh from Farmers</p>
        <a href="/products.html" class="hero-btn">Explore Our Products</a>
      </div>
      <!-- Background Image/Video -->
      <div class="hero-media">
        <img src="/assets/images/home-img.jpg" alt="Guntur Chillies" class="hero-image">
        <!-- If using video, replace the img tag with the below video code -->
        <!-- <video autoplay muted loop class="hero-video">
          <source src="your-video.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        </video> -->
      </div>
    </section>

    <h4 class="custom-order-info">
      <br />
      Customized orders are available upon request.<br />
      We provide retail packaging in jute and PP materials, with options <br />in 5kg, 10kg, and 25kg sizes.<br />
      For detailed pricing information on our red chillies and chilli powder, <br />please contact us today.<br />
      <br />
    </h4>

    <section class="product-slider">
      <div class="slider-container">
        <!-- Slide 1 -->
        <div class="slide">
          <img src="/assets/images/teja2.jpeg" alt="Teja S17 Chilli">
          <div class="slide-content">
            <h3>Teja S17 Dried Red Chilli</h3>
            <p>Known for its high heat and vibrant color. Ideal for adding a fiery kick to your dishes</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Slide 2 -->
        <div class="slide">
          <img src="/assets/images/bydgi1.jpg" alt="Byadgi Chilli">
          <div class="slide-content">
            <h3>Byadgi Dried Red Chilli</h3>
            <p>Less spicy but rich in color, perfect for flavorful dishes and culinary garnishing</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Slide 3 -->
        <div class="slide">
          <img src="/assets/images/cp.jpg" alt="Chilli Powder">
          <div class="slide-content">
            <h3>Pure Guntur Chilli Powder</h3>
            <p>Finely ground from premium Guntur chillies, this powder adds flavor and heat to every bite</p>
            <!-- <a href="#buy" class="btn">Buy Now</a>
            <a href="#learn" class="btn secondary">Learn More</a> -->
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="slide">
          <img src="/assets/images/334_2.jpeg" alt="334 Chilli">
          <div class="slide-content">
            <h3>334 Dried Red Chilli</h3>
            <p>Moderately spicy with vibrant red color, ideal for enhancing flavor and adding a rich hue to culinary dishes</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="slide">
          <img src="/assets/images/341.png" alt="341 Chilli">
          <div class="slide-content">
            <h3>341 Dried Red Chilli</h3>
            <p>High in heat with a deep red color, perfect for adding intense spice and bold flavor to a variety of dishes</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="slide">
          <img src="/assets/images/armoor.jpeg" alt="armoor Chilli">
          <div class="slide-content">
            <h3>Armoor Dried Red Chilli</h3>
            <p>Medium spiciness with a bright red color, ideal for adding balanced heat and rich flavor to curries and sauces</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="slider-nav">
        <button onclick="previousSlide()">Previous</button>
        <button onclick="nextSlide()">Next</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- why-choose-us -->
    <div class="whychooseus-container">
      <p class="whychooseus">Why Choose Us?</p>

      <!-- Badges Section -->
      <div class="badges-container" id="badgesContainer">
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class='h-insta'>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/guntur_red_chillies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" title="Follow us" class="h-insta-btn">
        <img src="/assets/images/insta-logo.png" alt="Instagram" width="240" height="240" />
      </a>
      <h3>Stay Connected with Us on Instagram!</h3>
      <h7>We'd love to share more about our passion for dried red chillies and give you a behind-the-scenes look at how we source the finest chillies straight from farmers. Follow us on Instagram for updates, exclusive offers, and a peek into our journey. We can't wait to connect with you!</h7>
    </div>

  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Devika Exim",
      "url": "https://devikaexim.in",
      "logo": "https://devikaexim.in/assets/images/logo-no-bg.png",
      "description": "Devika Exim is a leading supplier of high-quality red chillies sourced directly from Guntur.",
      "contactPoint": {
        "@type": "ContactPoint",
        "telephone": "+91-8341339975",
        "contactType": "Customer Service",
        "areaServed": "IN",
        "availableLanguage": "English, Telugu"
      },
      "sameAs": [
        "https://www.instagram.com/guntur_red_chillies",
        "https://www.facebook.com/srexportchilli"
      ],
      "product": {
        "@type": "Product",
        "name": "Dry Red Chillies",
        "image": "https://devikaexim.in/assets/images/logo-no-bg.png",
        "description": "High-quality dry red chillies sourced from Guntur, known for their rich flavor and heat.",
        "brand": {
          "@type": "Brand",
          "name": "Devika Exim"
        },
        "offers": {
          "@type": "Offer",
          "url": "https://devikaexim.in/products.html",
          "priceCurrency": "INR",
          "price": "16000",
          "itemCondition": "https://schema.org/NewCondition",
          "availability": "https://schema.org/InStock"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
